quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  36,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  36,1,Yaa-Seeen
  36,2,qasam hai quran ki jo hikmat se bhara howa hai
  36,3,ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) be shak tum payghambaroon mein se ho
  36,4,seedhay raste par
  36,5,yeh khuday-e ) ghalib ( aur ) meharban ne nazilkiya hai
  36,6,taakay tum un logon ko jin ke baap dada ko mutnabba nahikiya gaya tha mutnabba kardo woh ghaflat mein parre hue hain
  36,7,un mein se aksar par ( khuda ki ) baat poori hochuki hai so woh imaan nahi layein ge
  36,8,hum ne un ki gardnon mein taoq daal rakhay hain aur woh thoriu taq ( phansay hu-ay hain ) to un ke sir ulal rahay hain (uthay howay hain)
  36,9,aur hum ne un ke agay bhi deewar bana di aur un ke peechay bhi. phir un par parda daal diya to yeh dekh nahi satke
  36,10,aur tum un ko nasiyaat karo ya nah karo un ke liye barabar hai woh imaan nahi laane ke
  36,11,tum to sirf is shakhs ko nasiyaat kar saktay ho jo nasiyaat ki pairwi kere aur khuda se ghaybanh daray so is ko mughfirat aur barray sawab ki basharat suna do
  36,12,be shak hum mardon ko zindah karen ge aur jo kuch woh agay bhaij chuke aur ( jo ) un ke nishaan peechay reh gay hum un ko qalamband kar lete hain. aur har cheez ko hum ne kitaab roshan ( yani looh mehfooz ) mein likh rakha hai .
  36,13,aur un se gaon walon ka qissa bayan karo jab un ke paas paighambar aeye
  36,14,( yani ) jab hum ne un ki taraf do ( paighambar ) beje to unhon ne un ko jhtlaya. phir hum ne teesray se taqwiyat di to unhon ne kaha ke hum tumhari taraf paighambar ho kar aeye hain
  36,15,woh bolay ke tum ( aur kuch ) nahi magar hamari terhan ke aadmi ( ho ) aur khuda ne koi cheez nazil nahi ki tum mehez jhoot boltay ho
  36,16,unhon ne kaha ke hamara perwar-digaar jaanta hai ke hum tumhari taraf ( pegham day kar ) beje gay hain
  36,17,aur hamaray zimmay to saaf saaf pouncha dena hai aur bas
  36,18,woh bolay ke hum tum ko namubarak samajte hain. agar tum baz nah aao ge to hum tumhe sangsar kar dein ge aur tum ko hum se dukh dainay wala azaab puhanche ga
  36,19,unhon ne kaha ke tumhari nahosat tumahray sath hai.kiya is liye ke tum ko nasiyaat ki gayi. balkay tum aisay log ho jo hadd se tajawaz kar gay ho
  36,20,aur shehar ke parlay kinare se aik aadmi dorta howa aaya kehnay laga ke ae meri qoum payghambaroon ke peechay chalo
  36,21,aison ke jo tum se sila nahi mangte aur woh seedhay raste par hain
  36,22,aur mujhekiya hai mein is ki parastish nah karoon jis ne mujhe pedakiya aur isi ki taraf tum ko lout kar jana hai
  36,23,kiya mein un ko chore kar ouron ko mabood bunun? agar khuda mere haq mein nuqsaan karna chahay to un ki sifarish mujhe kuch bhi faida nah day sakay aur nah woh mujh ko churra hi saken
  36,24,tab to mein Sarih gumraahi mein mubtala hogaya
  36,25,mein tumahray perwar-digaar par imaan laya hon so meri baat sun rakho
  36,26,hukum howa ke bahisht mein daakhil hoja. bola kash! meri qoum ko khabar ho
  36,27,ke khuda ne mujhe bakhash diya aur izzat walon meinkiya
  36,28,aur hum ne is ke baad is ki qoum par koi lashkar nahi utaara aur nah hum aُtarne walay they hi
  36,29,woh to sirf aik chngharh thi (aatsheen ) so woh ( is se ) nagahan bujh kar reh gay
  36,30,bundon par afsos hai ke un ke paas koi paighambar nahi aata magar is se tamaskhur karte hain
  36,31,kiya unhon ne nahi dekha ke hum ne un se pehlay bohat se logon ko halaak kardiya tha ab woh un ki taraf lout kar nahi ayen ge
  36,32,aur sab ke sab hamaray rubaroo haazir kiye jayen ge
  36,33,aur aik nishani un ke liye zameen murda hai ke hum ne is ko zindahkiya aur is mein se anaaj aُgaya. phir yeh is mein se khatay hain
  36,34,aur is mein khajoron aur angarro ke baagh peda kiye aur is mein chashmay jari kardiye
  36,35,taakay yeh un ke phal khayen aur un ke hathon ne to un ko nahi banaya to phir yeh shukar kyun nahi karte ?
  36,36,woh khuda pak hai jis ne zameen ki nabataat ke aur khud un ke aur jin cheezon ki un ko khabar nahi sab ke jore banaye
  36,37,aur aik nishani un ke liye raat hai ke is mein se hum din ko khech letay hain to is waqt un par andhera chhaa jata hai
  36,38,aur Sooraj apne muqarrar raste par chalta rehta hai. yeh ( khuday-e ) ghalib aur Dana ka ( muqarrarkiya howa ) andaza hai
  36,39,aur chaand ki bhi hum ne manzilain muqarrar kar dein yahan taq ke ( ghatte ghatte ) khajoor ki purani shaakh ki terhan ho jata hai
  36,40,nah to Sooraj hi se ho sakta hai ke chaand ko ja pakdae aur nah raat hi din se pehlay askati hai. aur sab apne apne dairay mein teer rahay hain
  36,41,aur aik nishani un ke liye yeh hai ke hum ne un ki aulaad ko bhari hui kashti mein sawaarkiya
  36,42,aur un ke liye waisi hi aur cheeze peda kee jin par woh sawaar hotay hain
  36,43,aur agar hum chahain to un ko ghark kar dein. phir nah to un ka koi faryaad ras howa aur nah un ko rihayi miley
  36,44,magar yeh hamari rehmat aur aik muddat taq ke faiday hain
  36,45,aur jab un se kaha jata hai ke jo tumahray agay aur jo tumahray peechay hai is se daro taakay tum par rehamkiya jaye
  36,46,aur un ke paas un ke perwar-digaar ki koi nishani nahi aati magar is se munh phair letay hain
  36,47,aur jab un se kaha jata hai ke jo rizaq khuda ne tum ko diya hai is mein se kharch karo. to kafir mominoun se kehte hain ke bhala hum un logon ko khana khilain jin ko agar khuda chahta to khud khula deta. tum to Sarih ghalti mein ho
  36,48,aur kehte hain agar tum sach kehte ho to yeh wada kab ( poora ) hoga ?
  36,49,yeh to aik chngharh ke munhtazir hain jo un ko is haal mein ke baahum jhagar rahay hon ge a pakray gi
  36,50,phir nah wasiyat kar saken ge aur nah apne ghar walon mein wapas ja sakain ge
  36,51,aur ( jis waqt ) sor phonka jaye ga yeh qabron se ( nikal kar ) apne perwar-digaar ki taraf daud parrin ge
  36,52,kahin ge ae hai hamein hamari khabgahon se kis ne ( jaga ) aُthaya? yeh wohi to hai jis ka khuda ne wadakiya tha aur payghambaroon ne sach kaha tha
  36,53,sirf aik zor ki aawaz ka hona hoga ke sab ke sab hamaray rubaroo آhazir hon ge
  36,54,is roz kisi shakhs par kuch zulm nahikiya jaye ga aur tum ko badla waisa hi miley ga jaisay tum kaam karte they
  36,55,ahal jannat is roz aish wa nishaat ke mashghelay mein hon ge
  36,56,woh bhi aur un ki biwiyan bhi saayon mein takhton par takiye lagaye baithy hon ge
  36,57,wahan un ke liye meway aur jo chahain ge ( mojood hoga )
  36,58,perwar-digaar meharban ki taraf se salam ( kaha jaye ga )
  36,59,aur gunahgaro! aaj allag ho jao
  36,60,ae aadam ki aulaad hum ne tum se keh nahi diya tha ke shetan ko nah poojna woh tumhara khula dushman hai
  36,61,aur yeh ke meri hi ibadat karna. yahi seedha rasta hai
  36,62,aur is ne tum mein se bohat si khalqat ko gumraah kardiya tha. tokiya tum samajte nahi they ?
  36,63,yahi woh jahannum hai jis ki tumhe khabar di jati hai
  36,64,( so ) jo tum kufar karte rahay ho is ke badlay aaj is mein daakhil hojao
  36,65,aaj hum un ke monhon par mohar laga den ge aur jo kuch yeh karte rahay they un ke haath hum se bayan kar dein ge aur un ke paon ( is ki ) gawahi den ge
  36,66,aur agar hum chahain to un ki aankhon ko mita kar ( andha kar ) den. phir yeh raste ko dorhin to kahan dekh saken ge
  36,67,aur agar hum chahain to un ki jagah par un ki soorten badal den phir wahan se nah agay ja sakain aur nah ( peechay ) lout saken
  36,68,aur jis ko hum barri Umar dete hain to usay khalqat mein ondha kardete hain tokiya yeh samajte nahi ?
  36,69,aur hum ne un ( paighambar ) ko shair goi nahi sikhayi aur nah woh un ko Shayaan hai. yeh to mehez nasiyaat aur saaf saaf quran ( pur az hikmat ) hai
  36,70,taakay is shakhs ko jo zindah ho hadaayat ka rasta dukhaay aur kafiroon par baat poori hojaye
  36,71,kiya unhon ne nahi dekha ke jo cheeze hum ne apne hathon se banayen un mein se hum ne un ke liye charpaye peda kar diye aur yeh un ke maalik hain
  36,72,aur un ko un ke qaboo mein kardiya to koi to un mein se un ki sawari hai aur kisi ko yeh khatay hain
  36,73,aur un mein un ke liye ( aur ) faiday aur peenay ki cheeze hain. to yeh shukar kyun nahi karte ?
  36,74,aur unhon ne khuda ke siwa ( aur ) mabood bana liye hain ke shayad ( un se ) un ko madad puhanche
  36,75,( magar ) woh un ki madad ki ( hargiz ) taaqat nahi rakhtay. aur woh un ki fouj ho kar haazir kiye jayen ge
  36,76,to un ki baatein tumhe ghumnaak nah kar dein. yeh jo kuch chupatay aur jo kuch zahir karte hain hamein sab maloom hai
  36,77,kiya ensaan ne nahi dekha ke hum ne is ko nutfay se pedakiya. phir woh تڑاق پڑاق jhagrnay laga
  36,78,aur hamaray baray mein misalein bayan karne laga aur apni paidaiesh ko bhool gaya. kehnay laga ke ( jab ) haddiyan boseedah ho jaien gi to un ko kon zindah kere ga ?
  36,79,keh do ke un ko woh zindah kere ga jis ne un ko pehli baar pedakiya tha. aur woh sab qisam ka peda karna jaanta hai
  36,80,jis ne tumahray liye sabz darakht se aag peda ki phir tum is ( ki tehnion ko ragar kar un ) se aag nikaltay ho
  36,81,"bhala jis ne asmano aur zameen ko pedakiya,kiya woh is baat par Qadir nahi ke ( un ko phir ) waisay hi peda kar day. kyun nahi. aur woh to bara peda karne wala aur ilm wala hai"
  36,82,is ki shaan yeh hai ke jab woh kisi cheez ka iradah karta hai to is se farma deta hai ke hoja to woh hojati hai
  36,83,woh ( zaat ) pak hai jis ke haath mein har cheez ki badshahat hai aur isi ki taraf tum ko lout kar jana hai
